1
00:14:50,306 --> 00:14:51,932
That's right.

2
00:19:29,501 --> 00:19:31,336
See you.

3
00:50:06,211 --> 00:50:08,213
You're here! Right on time.

4
00:50:16,179 --> 00:50:20,350
Never in your life have you tasted
something so delicious, it's true. Wait....

5
00:50:21,601 --> 00:50:24,146
You're gonna die.

6
00:50:26,440 --> 00:50:27,733
No, thank you.

7
00:50:30,444 --> 00:50:32,112
Smell it!

8
00:50:32,279 --> 00:50:34,197
You can't say no, are you crazy?

9
00:50:39,286 --> 00:50:41,121
Very well. You're not hungry.

10
00:50:41,705 --> 00:50:42,914
That's your problem.

11
00:50:43,707 --> 00:50:48,670
This is a special recipe.
A family secret.

12
00:50:55,969 --> 00:50:56,970
I am Eduardo.

13
00:50:58,805 --> 00:51:02,184
And you must be Varga, no?

14
00:51:03,477 --> 00:51:06,521
They told me you were smart.
And look...

15
00:51:06,688 --> 00:51:09,524
...here you are, and you are.

16
00:51:39,596 --> 00:51:41,431
Come on, Varga. Let's go!

